Project by M.Winkens (m.winkens@fz-juelich.de)
Preprocessor-Commands for octree:

BIGTEST //Test the octree with a main with a HUGE Tree

OCDEBUGTEST //Activates ALL options under this one
OCTEST //Test the octree with a main

OCDEBUG //Activates ALL options UNDER this one


OCDRAW //Activate the output when any draw-function, but I would not recommend drawing all nodes for debug
OCINSERT //Activate the output for the insert
OCDELETE //Activate the output for deleting the OCTree
OCCLEAR //Activate the output for clear


